content: The interview went well. They appreciated my ethical stance on AI transparency. Now it's the waiting game.
Received the offer! I'm now a lead quantitative analyst. Time to make an impact with AI-driven models.
First week on the job. I'm integrating my sentiment analysis into our trading strategies. It's challenging but exhilarating.
Had a minor setback. My algorithm had a false positive signal. But it's a learning curve. Back to the drawing board to refine.
Presented my project to the team. They see potential but raised concerns about ethical implications. It's back to the drawing board, but with more support.
Collaborated with a mentor on an AI ethics paper. We're proposing a framework for ethical trading algorithms. It's complex but necessary.
The team is now on board with my vision. We're working on a pilot project to implement ethical AI trading. It's a slow process, but we're moving forward.
Just had a breakthrough. Our pilot project showed promising results. The firm is excited about the potential. It's a step towards my goal of revolutionizing trading with AI.
